  "body": "### Component\n\nForge\n\n### Have you ensured that all of these are up to date?\n\n- [X] Foundry\n- [X] Foundryup\n\n### What version of Foundry are you on?\n\nforge 0.2.0 (3e12d88 2023-11-17T00:28:12.734710000Z)\n\n### What command(s) is the bug in?\n\nforge script\n\n### Operating System\n\nmacOS (Intel)\n\n### Describe the bug\n\nScript estimates 5$, actual cost is 5cents. For 5$, I started researching what might be the problem (high gas price or wrong contract?)\r\n\r\nIn the end, the forge script predicted a price that is 100x higher than actual\r\n\r\n```\r\nforge script script/mainnet/Script.s.sol:AddProUsers \\\r\n  --rpc-url $ARB_MAINNET \\\r\n  --ledger \\\r\n  --sender 0xme \\\r\n  --broadcast -vvvv --verify\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n```\r\n==========================\r\n\r\nChain 42161\r\n\r\nEstimated gas price: 3.2 gwei\r\n\r\nEstimated total gas used for script: 907546\r\n\r\nEstimated amount required: 0.0029041472 ETH\r\n\r\n==========================\r\n\r\n###\r\nFinding wallets for all the necessary addresses...\r\n##\r\nSending transactions [0 - 0].\r\n⠁ [00:00:47] [###############################################################################################################################] 1/1 txes (0.0s)\r\n⠉ [00:00:06] [###########################################################################################################################] 1/1 receipts (0.0s)\r\n##### arbitrum\r\n✅  [Success]Hash: 0x3bd...\r\nBlock: 151...\r\nPaid: 0.0000586377 ETH (586377 gas * 0.1 gwei)\r\n```",
